{
  "info": {
    "name": "KODE IoT Monitoring API",
    "description": "REST API untuk sistem monitoring kebakaran dan asap berbasis IoT.\n\n**Base URL:** `https://your-render-app.onrender.com`\n\n**Authentication:** Endpoint POST /api/data memerlukan header `x-api-key`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiKey",
      "value": "KODE_IOT_SECRET_KEY_2024",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Root",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get API Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": [""]
            },
            "description": "Menampilkan informasi dasar API dan daftar endpoint yang tersedia."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sensor Data",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Latest Sensor Data",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/data",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "data"]
            },
            "description": "Mengambil data sensor terbaru yang dikirim oleh ESP32.\n\n**Response:**\n- `ppm` (number): Kadar asap dalam PPM\n- `adc` (number): Nilai ADC dari sensor asap\n- `flame` (number): Status sensor api (0=api terdeteksi, 1=aman)\n- `dist` (number): Jarak dari sensor ultrasonik (cm)\n- `water_pct` (number): Persentase volume air\n- `pump` (number): Status pompa (0=mati, 1=nyala)\n- `timestamp` (string): Waktu data terakhir diperbarui (ISO 8601)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Post Sensor Data (ESP32)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-api-key",
                "value": "{{apiKey}}",
                "type": "text",
                "description": "API Key untuk autentikasi ESP32"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ppm\": 120.5,\n  \"adc\": 800,\n  \"flame\": 0,\n  \"dist\": 15.3,\n  \"water_pct\": 75.5,\n  \"pump\": 1\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/data",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "data"]
            },
            "description": "Mengirim data sensor dari ESP32 ke server.\n\n**Headers:**\n- `x-api-key` (required): API Key untuk autentikasi\n\n**Body Parameters:**\n- `ppm` (number, required): Kadar asap dalam PPM\n- `adc` (number): Nilai ADC dari sensor asap\n- `flame` (number, required): Status sensor api (0=api terdeteksi, 1=aman)\n- `dist` (number, required): Jarak dari sensor ultrasonik (cm)\n- `water_pct` (number): Persentase volume air\n- `pump` (number): Status pompa (0=mati, 1=nyala)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "History",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Data History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/history",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "history"]
            },
            "description": "Mengambil 100 data sensor terakhir yang tersimpan di server.\n\n**Response:** Array of sensor data objects dengan format yang sama seperti GET /api/data."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Memeriksa status server dan informasi uptime.\n\n**Response:**\n- `status` (string): Status server ('online')\n- `uptime` (number): Waktu server berjalan (detik)\n- `lastUpdate` (string): Waktu update terakhir (ISO 8601)\n- `readingsStored` (number): Jumlah data yang tersimpan"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Set environment variables if not already set",
          "if (!pm.environment.get('baseUrl')) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('baseUrl', 'http://localhost:3000');",
          "}",
          "if (!pm.environment.get('apiKey')) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('apiKey', 'KODE_IOT_SECRET_KEY_2024');",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Test response time",
          "pm.test('Response time is less than 2000ms', function () {",
          "    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(2000);",
          "});",
          "",
          "// Test status code",
          "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
          "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
          "});",
          "",
          "// Test response is JSON",
          "pm.test('Response is JSON', function () {",
          "    pm.response.to.have.header('Content-Type', /json/);",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
